isolate" title="Language isolate">Isolates</a>:</b> <a href="/wiki/Andamanese_languages" title="Andamanese languages">Andamanese</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Burushaski" title="Burushaski">Burushaski</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kalto_language" title="Kalto language">Kalto</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kusunda_language" title="Kusunda language">Kusunda</a>&#160;• <b><a href="/wiki/Mon-Khmer_languages" title="Mon-Khmer languages">Mon-Khmer</a>:</b> <a href="/wiki/Khasi_language" title="Khasi language">Khasi</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Nicobarese" title="Nicobarese" class="mw-redirect">Nicobarese</a>&#160;• <b><a href="/wiki/Munda_languages" title="Munda languages">Munda</a>:</b> <a href="/wiki/Ho_language" title="Ho language">Ho</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Korku_language" title="Korku language" class="mw-redirect">Korku</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mundari_language" title="Mundari language">Mundari</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Santali_language" title="Santali language">Santali</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sora_language" title="Sora language">Sora</a>&#160;• <b>European influence:</b> <a href="/wiki/Indian_English" title="Indian English">English</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Indian_French" title="Indian French">French</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sri_Lanka_Indo-Portuguese_language" title="Sri Lanka Indo-Portuguese language">Portuguese</a>&#160;• <b><a href="/wiki/Tibeto-Burman" title="Tibeto-Burman" class="mw-redirect">Tibeto-Burman</a>:</b> <a href="/wiki/Ao_language" title="Ao language" class="mw-redirect">Ao</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bodo_language" title="Bodo language">Bodo</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Garo_language" title="Garo language">Garo</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kokborok_language" title="Kokborok language">Kokborok</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Meitei_language" title="Meitei language">Meitei</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mizo_language" title="Mizo language">Mizo</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Nepal_Bhasa" title="Nepal Bhasa">Nepal Bhasa</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sikkimese_language" title="Sikkimese language" class="mw-redirect">Sikkimese</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tenyidie_language" title="Tenyidie language" class="mw-redirect">Tenyidie</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tibetan_language" title="Tibetan language" class="mw-redirect">Tibetan</a></div>
